<TEXT>
the former host of the pennsylvania lotterys 
tv drawing who was convicted in a scheme to rig the game is making 
a television comeback as host of a bowling show 
i was apprehensive you could say i still am nick perry 
said theres bound to be somebody out there dissatisfied with my 
coming back 
