matt thompson is first and foremost a 
shooter and if the soldier framed in his camera lens dies in 
combat well its going to make a great picture 
thompson clutching his cameras is tramping through the jungle 
aware of the viet cong stalking him and the american soldiers 
around him yet concentrating on getting the shot 
the shot thats going to amaze his wire service bosses back in 
new york the shot thats going to land on the front page of every 
