<TEXT>
the diver jacques mayol believes dolphins are 
the smartest animals around and he tries to emulate their way of 
life 
that is my hobby to see how we are related to the dolphins 
said mayol the inspiration for the film big blue 
its examples should always be followed by man its purity and 
simplicity its respect of its own behavior with nature he who 
lives in harmony with nature can only do good 
big blue directed by luc besson chronicles mayols life 
from his childhood mayol however points out that the film 
differs greatly from what actually happened 
you cant make a movie totally based on my own life it could 
be a little boring he said it would be too much like a 
documentary too scientific too philosophical 
in big blue he grows up in greece and has a diver for a 
father however mayol was actually born in the orient and later 
went to greece to study his father was not a diver but an 
architect and did not like to swim 
besson made a psychological transfer of his youth in greece 
he said he distorted everything which doesnt matter because 
its a movie i just accept it like dolphins do 
much of big blue is devoted to mayols friendly rivalry with 
enzo maiorca an italian free diver maiorca whose name was 
changed to molinari in big blue is determined to dive deeper 
than mayol and dies at the end of the film the real enzo maiorca 
is alive 
hes very proud very much like hes depicted in the film 
mayol said he claims he hasnt seen it but i knows hes seen 
it he was irritated to the point where hes going to attempt to 
beat me again 
the truth is that this rivalry after 22 years still exists 
the actor jeanmarc barr portrays mayol in big blue 
hes almost like a son to me mayol said i admired his 
desire and his total sincerity in trying to supplicate the little 
he knew about me it was fantastic what he did physically he dove 
day after day 
mayol says it was bessons idea to make the movie 
luc went to see me and i thought it was a fabulous thing i 
couldnt believe it he was just a kid 
the film has already been released in europe and has brought 
