the umbrella organization of 84 trade unions was 4577 million to 
4042 million a tiny margin that reflected the split in british 
organized labor over the controversial government program union 
chiefs wield huge voting blocks based on membership 
neil kinnock leader of the opposition labor party had joined 
the tuc leadership in appealing against a boycott saying it would 
portray the labor movement as uncaring about the jobless 
but the proboycott camp claimed that the 15billionpound 
255 billion employment training scheme launched monday was 
