lambert inc subroto didnt seem to be getting anywhere 
the middle east economic survey an influential weekly published 
in nicosia cyprus reported last week that total opec production 
was estimated at 20 million barrels a day more than 35 million 
barrels over the cartels official ceiling 
the ceasefire between the persian gulf rivals after eight years 
of fighting frees iran and iraq to rebuild their wardamaged oil 
industries raising the prospect of a fresh surge in oil production 
and a fall in crude prices 
