opecs ability to bring iraq back under its discipline 
iraq during the war past ignored its opec daily production quota 
of 154 million barrels demanding a share equal to irans 237 
million barrels a day iraq pumps an estimated 28 million barrels 
a day analysts say 
theres too much oil right now opec is showing a complete 
lack of discipline said peter beutel assistant director of the 
